All MELEE weapons I'll agree with, but not bows.  Clearly the ranger is supposed to me the bow miester, with disc's and AA in that direction.  Why our archery caps at 240, I have no idea though.<br>
<br>
Anyway, I'm blown away by warriors who don't posess bows.  While conciously maxing archery seems a bit painful for warriors, what better range weapon / tagging tool is there?<br>
<br>
For warriors that may be considering archery, a good cheap bow is the Shaped Shadewood Compound (range 200).  Shouldn't be more than a coupla hundred platinum tops in the bazaar.  Froglok forager also drops a decent starter bow.<br>
<br>
If you are exping and not the puller, just start plinking the mobs as they are pulled.  An arrow or two a mob will raise your skills in no time.<br>
